me":"2019-09-19T05:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e6b10d5a8cb3c09be61b94b3b20f57d7e27577","tid":1580452,"uid":32983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"mindfuck<br />\n「順服掌權者，凡掌權的，都是神所命定的 」<br />\n咁中共港共係咪上帝命定既呢"},{"pid":"fab2083e5eb000387178babcea1c33082d316329","tid":1580452,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"南京大屠殺是對的， 因為死的都是異教徒"},{"pid":"5f94259614fb2b18270cba69203668e93ebd468f","tid":1580452,"uid":67332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他聲稱，唯有政府強逼信徒做違反聖經的行為，例如禁止祈禱和傳福音，才能反抗；</span></span><br />\n中共拆十字架，而港共under中共，所以。。。"},{"pid":"6c1a3a69fd720798be600270835410bc7afc5cb5","tid":1580452,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:55:24.000Z","msg":"邪教發現"},{"pid":"b232a2d2bfd0e13ec596ff3f9828cdb0b7fd6d74","tid":1580452,"uid":181102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"權威性人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}